A Kirist ned yaa bõe? Sokre: A Kirist ned yaa bõe? Leokre: Gom-biisã-bilgr sebr bilgame t’a Kirist ned yaa “ned sen yaagd-a nor n togsdẽ tɩ yẽ tẽeda a Zezi wa Kristã wala Wẽnd-tũudm nĩng sen tĩk a Zezi goamã n tũud-a wã.” Hal baa bilgrã sãn n yaa soamã, wa gom-biis-bilgr sɛb wʋsg mẽ sen bilgi, a zulmã ka ta Wẽnnaam sebrã sen yaa sɩd goamã bilgrã zulm sen ta zĩig ningã n wilgid a Kirist tẽed sen yaa soab ye. Yaa nõor a tab la b pʋd “Kirist ned” gom-bilã yʋʋr Kãab Paalgã pʋga. (Tʋʋmã 11:26; 26:28;
